'''曼格拉谷'''（'''Mangala Valles'''），又稱'''曼加拉谷'''，是[[火星|火星]]上一处複雜的十字交叉河道區域，位於[[塔爾西斯|塔爾西斯]]地區，長度828公里，生成於[[亞馬遜紀|亞馬遜紀]]。名稱來自於[[梵語|梵語]]的火星。

==地形==
這個區域一般被認為是災難性洪水從火星表面大量流過以後冲刷而成的[[溢出河道|溢出河道]]。洪水的由來可能是因為板塊的張裂並在源頭形成[[地塹|地塹]]的緣故，造成[[冰凍圈|冰凍圈]]下受壓[[含水層|含水層]]破裂使地下水大量流出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.msss.com/http/ps/channels/channels.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-03-28 |archive-date=2017-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428065907/http://www.msss.com/http/ps/channels/channels.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Carr2006">{{cite book|author=Michael H. Carr|title=The surface of Mars|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=uLHlJ6sjohwC|accessdate=21 March 2011|year=2006|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=9780521872010|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103131155/http://books.google.com/books?id=uLHlJ6sjohwC|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Carr, M.  1979.  Formation of martian flood features by release of water from confined aquifers.  J. Geophys. Res.  84:  2995-3007.</ref><ref>ISBN 978-0-521-87501-0</ref><ref>Hanna, J. and R. Phillips.  2005.  Tectonic pressurization of aquifers in the formation of Mangala and Athabasca Valles on Mars.  LPSC XXXVI.  Abstract 2261.</ref>。

曼格拉谷中有許多風蝕的山嶺或[[雅丹地貌|雅丹地貌]]占據了峽谷許多區域<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://photojournal.jpl.nasa.gov/catalog/PIA03827 |title=Catalog Page for PIA03827 |access-date=2012-03-28 |archive-date=2021-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322194657/https://photojournal.jpl.nasa.gov/catalog/PIA03827 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.uapress.arizona.edu/onlinebks/mars/chap12.htm The Planet Mars: A History of Observation and Discovery. Chapter 12: Mariner 9. University of Arizona Press] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141004105217/http://www.uapress.arizona.edu/onlinebks/MARS/CHAP12.HTM |date=2014-10-04 }}</ref>。

==文學作品中的曼格拉谷==
曼格拉谷出現在[[麥可·克萊頓|麥可·克萊頓]]的小說《[[神秘之球|神秘之球]]》中。[[史蒂芬·巴克斯特|史蒂芬·巴克斯特]]的小說《[[遠航_(史蒂芬·巴克斯特)|遠航]]》中當地是首次載人火星任務的登陸地。

